==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Warper
<hw>Warp"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, warps or twists out of shape.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, forms yarn or thread into
warps or webs for the loom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Warping</ent>⟦br⟧
